Lgm_CTrans* Lgm_CopyCTrans ( Lgm_CTrans *  s  ) 

The Lgm_CTrans structure has pointers in it, so simple asignments (e.g.

*t = *s) are dangerous. Here we make sure that the target gets an independent copy of the structure.
